    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015190/extras/38db2cadb2a5e190e467bb8eaaf3694d.poster.avif?t=1758463117\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015190/extras/38db2cadb2a5e190e467bb8eaaf3694d.webm?t=1758463117\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015190/extras/38db2cadb2a5e190e467bb8eaaf3694d.mp4?t=1758463117\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Rap Pop Jump Core</strong> 是一款硬核动作平台游戏，需要不断移动、快速决策和同时与敌人战斗。沉浸在充满活力的 Rap Pop Jump Core 城市中，唯一的移动方式是从一个平台跳到另一个平台。 一步走错，你将坠入命运。使用您的敏捷性和技能快速导航并逃离城市。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015190/extras/2641f878b6932c3e5fb7193f34360e8a.poster.avif?t=1758463117\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015190/extras/2641f878b6932c3e5fb7193f34360e8a.webm?t=1758463117\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015190/extras/2641f878b6932c3e5fb7193f34360e8a.mp4?t=1758463117\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >主要特点：</h2></strong><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >紧张的动作：</h2>参与快速的跳台和战斗，快速反应和准确决策对于生存和进步至关重要。<br></li><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >动态环境：</h2>探索一个充满活力且不断变化的城市景观，布满平台，每个平台都需要精确的时间和策略才能成功导航。<br></li><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >惊险挑战：</h2>面对各种敌人和障碍，增加难度层次，测试您的技能并保持警觉。<br></li><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >基于技能的游戏玩法：</h2>掌握快速移动和战斗的艺术，利用您的能力在试图逃离城市的危险高度时超过敌人并避免致命跌落。<ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul></li></ul>",
